<div class = "header"> FAQ </div>
<div class = "card">
	<ul>
  	<li>How do I sign up for a lesson?</li>
  		<p class = "answer"> Go to "Looking to Learn" from the home screen and pick an activity that you want to learn! </p>
  	<li>How do I pay for a lesson?</li>
  		<p class = "answer"> Go to your profile from the home screen and look through your "Learning History" to see any lessons that still need payment!</p>
  	<li>How do I review a lesson?</li>
  		<p class = "answer"> Go to your profile from the home screen and look through your "Learning History" to review any past lessons!</p>
  	<li>How do I send a teacher a message?</li>
  		<p class = "answer"> You can email them through our "Hiring Screen". To get there, go to "Looking to Teach", select an activity and a teacher and then click "Hire"!</p>
</ul>
